知唔知邊到有咁長嘅lan 線買？</blockquote><br />\n黄金大把啦"},{"pid":"7f3438a75cc07edb47d00926b84a0325e7bbf986","tid":180472,"uid":28168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:23:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>asus router la</blockquote><br />\n已經買多左個router ，都係唔掂，間房太恐怖，電話都收得好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n證明你間房有多大干擾源<br />\n<br />\ncheck下比較好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你間房放左D咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0071f106fd30716d44d3be3e894a8841a68167ec","tid":180472,"uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:02:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾長都有 賣電腦野既細鋪 同佢講佢會幫你剪</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打"},{"pid":"37527dbf8a6bac29139e746e96149623e6eadb0e","tid":180472,"uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:04:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買多個repeater 得唔得</blockquote><br />\n我之前將舊果個router set過嚟,當repeater 咁用，但效果唔多好，今次想買多條lan線直接連，唔洗穿牆，應該快好多"},{"pid":"d9d5ef226451aaecc22e00a23cb1805dff65ddad","tid":180472,"uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:11:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>asus router la</blockquote><br />\n已經買多左個router ，都係唔掂，間房太恐怖，電話都收得好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n證明你間房有多大干擾源<br />\n<br />\ncheck下比較好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你間房放左D咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實岩岩先同屋企人換房嚟，果時房入面得一張床，其他咩都冇放，已經收得好差，而家都係多左張書枱<br />\n間房就四四方方，牆後面就放左router，居然收得一兩格<br />\n雖然牆都幾厚下，入面應該有電線、電話線、電視線等等，可能有唔少干擾"},{"pid":"e4334f9d3c6a86180b8485ad7c4f931dbad7fb2b","tid":180472,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T09:59:45.000Z","msg":"買d flat cat6 線<br />\n沿牆脚線用雙面膠紙黏都得<br />\n<br />\n穿房門底都無問題<br />\n<br />\n買20米都唔駛100蚊"},{"pid":"f9b61c209f8e69ec61a7a5030cf6f65ae89e7579","tid":180472,"uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T12:14:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買d flat cat6 線<br />\n沿牆脚線用雙面膠紙黏都得<br />\n<br />\n穿房門底都無問題<br />\n<br />\n買20米都唔駛100蚊</blockquote><br />\n係，咁岩今日已經去左黃金買flat cat6 ，效果非常好，終於唔洗再忍受果一兩格仔嘅wifi 啦"}]}